(60, 'default', 'created', 12, 'App\\Article', 1, 'App\\User', '{\"attributes\":{\"judul\":\"Latest Articles Regarding the Development of IT (Information Technology)\",\"slug\":\"latest-articles-regarding-the-development-of-it-information-technology\",\"konten\":\"<pre>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\\\">Over time, the use of technology has been adopted in almost all sectors of human life. In social life, information is one of the important objects that will come into direct contact with the public (the wider community). Various things that are new, dynamic and innovative are its main characteristics. Furthermore, this understanding also explains how important the role of information as a bridge for change. Based on this phenomenon, it can be said that almost all of our lives cannot be separated from it, so that everything related to its procurement must be done.<\\/span>\\r\\n<\\/pre>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<pre>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\\\">Information technology (IT) has a broad scope. When we review this theme it will usually connect other aspects outside it which in reality are interrelated with each other, for example information and communication technology. Two themes that will outline intersect each other. In general, the understanding of information technology or IT is all matters relating to the mechanism of using certain devices to process including information modification. In its application in the field, the latest articles about the development of IT find a variety of new phenomena that will always be interesting to watch. The mushrooming of internet cafes as internet service providers and various online news sites that are increasingly growing in number is the inevitable impact of IT deployment.<\\/span>\\r\\n<\\/pre>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\\\">The application of IT can also be identified in other areas that are needed to effectively convey the information itself. The fields that have applied information technology or IT are: Field of education The application of IT in the education sector can be identified by the existence of E-Learning, which is a kind of online learning system via the internet. With this facility it is possible for teachers and students to keep interacting without having to face-to-face for certain activities such as sending assignments and materials. Business Field Information technology (IT) has also been adopted in the business sector with products in the form of E-Commerce. The existence of E-Commerce is able to facilitate business people in conducting commerce activities online on the internet. All trading activities such as promotions, trading transactions can be accommodated properly and effectively. Banking sector The application of IT in the banking world can be seen from the mode of online banking transactions on the internet or more popularly called Internet Banking. With this facility the users can carry out certain activities such as checking balances, transferring money between accounts via their own devices such as computers, cellphones etc. Of course the relevant devices must be connected to the internet and have activated Internet Banking at the bank where they are customers. The use of Automated Teller Machines (ATMs) is also one of the applications of information technology that has been around for a long time. That was the discussion about the latest article about the development of IT (information technology) which we try to present to all readers. Indeed there are still examples of other IT applications, but here we only mention a few because of the various limitations that we have. Hopefully it will be a useful reference.<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"foto\":\"1m58SP_sampel.jpg\",\"category_id\":7,\"user_id\":1}}', '2019-09-19 03:07:00', '2019-09-19 03:07:00'),
